text: Humayun Kabir Chowdhury is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Naogaon-2. ==Career== Chowdhury was elected to parliament from Naogaon-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Naogaon District
title: Humayun Kabir Chowdhury
